title: Base
.description: Baseline run without climate policy/carbon tax

title: Trend
.description: Trend scenario with a -40% target for the EU in 2030 which was the former EU target before Fit-for-55

title: Bal
.description: Standard Ariadne scenario with -55% GHG in 2030 and GHG neutrality goal in 2050 for EU (incl. EU LULUCF sink), -65% GHG in 2030 and GHG neutrality goal in 2045 for Germany

title: Bal_Ampel
.description: Standard Ariadne scenario including targets of the coalition agreement of the Ampel from 2021

title: EnSec
.description: Energy security scenario with limits/taxes on PE gas consumption in Germany and reduced steel demand

title: EnSec_Ampel
.description: Energy security scenario including targets of the coalition agreement of the Ampel from 2021

title: Elec
.description: Scenario with high electrification, low H2 and synfuel imports

title: H2
.description: Scenario with high H2 and synfuel use, high H2 and synfuel imports
